@startuml
title ATM - Withdrawal Process

[*] --> Ready

state Ready
state WaitingForPIN
state ValidatingPIN
state WaitingForCustomerChoice
state ProcessingWithdrawal
state Dispensing
state Printing
state Ejecting
state Confiscating
state Terminating

Ready : entry / Display Welcome

WaitingForPIN : entry / Display Enter PIN

ValidatingPIN : entry / Validate PIN

WaitingForCustomerChoice : entry / Display Menu

ProcessingWithdrawal : entry / Process Withdrawal

Dispensing : entry / Dispense Cash

Printing : entry / Print Receipt

Ejecting : entry / Eject Card

Confiscating : entry / Confiscate Card

Terminating : entry / Reset System

Ready --> WaitingForPIN : Card Inserted / Get PIN

WaitingForPIN --> ValidatingPIN : PIN Entered / Validate PIN
ValidatingPIN --> WaitingForCustomerChoice : Valid PIN / Display Menu
ValidatingPIN --> Confiscating : Invalid PIN / Invalid PIN Prompt
ValidatingPIN --> Confiscating : Third Invalid PIN / Confiscate

WaitingForCustomerChoice --> ProcessingWithdrawal : Withdrawal Selected / Request Withdrawal, Display Wait

ProcessingWithdrawal --> Dispensing : Withdrawal Approved / Dispense Cash, Update Status
ProcessingWithdrawal --> Ejecting : Rejected / Eject

Dispensing --> Printing : Cash Dispensed / Print Receipt

Printing --> Ejecting : Receipt Printed / Eject

Ejecting --> Terminating : Card Ejected / Display Ejected
Confiscating --> Terminating : Card
Terminating --> [*] : Ready for Next User
@enduml
